description: Trident Brands Incorporated, together with its subsidiaries, focuses on developing branded consumer products and ingredients in the nutritional supplement, life sciences, and food and beverage categories in the United States and Canada. The company develops, markets, and sells a portfolio of DHA supplements under the Brain Armor brand. It also holds various banking facilities; and licenses associated with the manufacturing, importation, and sale of natural health and nutrition products. The company was formerly known as Sandfield Ventures Corp. and changed its name to Trident Brands Incorporated in July 2013. Trident Brands Incorporated was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Boca Raton, Florida.
ceo: Mr. Michael Jordan Friedman J.D., L.L.M.
